---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
import { Component as Dropdownmenu } from '../components/Dropdownmenu.tsx';
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
import { FeaturesSectionWithHoverEffects } from '../components/Features.tsx';
import Contactform from '@/components/contactform.astro';

const herosection = {
  heading: "WHERE CARS CHANGE HANDS - SEAMLESSLY",
  description: "Buy or rent your next ride with confidence.",
};

---

<Layout>

	<main>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/homeheroimg.png')] bg-cover bg-center max-w-screen object-cover h-[75vh]">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
		</div>


		<div class="container mx-auto lg:mt-42 mt-36 flex flex-col gap-5 items-center justify-center">

			<h1 class="relative z-10 sm:px-2 lg:px-0 lg:max-w-screen-2xl uppercase text-center text-accent text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl lg:text-5xl text-wrap">
				{herosection.heading}
			  </h1>
			  <p class="relative z-10 sm:px-2 lg:px-0 mx-auto mt-2 md:mt-4 lg:max-w-screen-2xl text-center text-accent md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-wrap">
				{herosection.description}
			  </p>
		</div>
	</main>

	<section class="container mx-auto relative z-10 lg:max-w-screen-lg max-w-screen-sm lg:mt-28 mt-20 bg-accent p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-5 items-center justify-center shadow-2xl">

		<p class="lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold uppercase text-destructive text-center text-wrap">Uncover Your Perfect Match</p>

		<p class="text-center text-wrap text-destructive lg:text-lg text-md max-w-2xl">
			Let’s find a car that matches your vibe! Answer a few quick questions so we can recommend rides that suit your personality and lifestyle.
		</p>
		

		<!-- Dropdown Menu -->
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-20">

			<span>
				How do you usually spend your weekends?
			</span>

			<Dropdownmenu/>
			
		</div>

		<a href="/buyacar">
			<Button className="bg-secondary hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground text-destructive font-semibold uppercase my-2">
			Take Complete Quiz
			</Button>
		</a>

	</section>
	
	<FeaturesSectionWithHoverEffects/>

	<img src="/aboutbmw.png" alt="aboutbmw" class="flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">


	<div id="about" class="container mx-auto flex flex-col gap-10 items-center justify-center relative z-10 mt-[-2rem] bg-secondary p-4 rounded-2xl lg:max-w-7xl my-5 shadow-xl">

		<h3 class="lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold uppercase text-destructive text-center text-wrap">About Us</h3>

		<div id="abouttext" class="flex flex-col gap-10">
			<p class="text-center text-wrap text-destructive lg:text-lg text-md max-w-5xl">
				Gearhwan is a car exchange and rental platform. The website offers users to buy new or used cars, sell their cars, and even 
				rent cars available on the website. The platform also recommends cars based on the user’s personality. A short questionnaire 
				is prepared to determine the buyer’s personality, which helps recommend cars that the user might enjoy driving. The website 
				also has a dedicated guides page, where users can find guides and tutorials on how to perfectly maintain their cars, and fix minor 
				issues by themselves. 
			</p>

			<p class="text-center text-wrap text-destructive lg:text-lg text-md max-w-5xl">
				The word “Gearhwan” is based on a combination of two words. “Gear” is referred as another word for a vehicle. “Hwan” is an abbreviation 
				taken from a Korean word “Gyohwan (교환)” which means exchange. The name of the platform can be translated to vehicle exchange, 
				highlighting the main services of buying and selling vehicles on one platform
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h3 class="lg:text-4xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold uppercase text-destructive text-center text-wrap my-20">Featured Cars</h3>


	<h3 class="lg:text-4xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold uppercase text-destructive text-center text-wrap my-20">Guides</h3>



	<h3 class="lg:text-4xl md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold uppercase text-destructive text-center text-wrap my-20">Trusted Brands</h3>
	<img src="/carbrandlogo.png" alt="carbrandlogo" class="flex items-center justify-center mx-auto my-20">

	<Contactform/>









</Layout>
